<a id="decision.surface-authority"></a>
### Decision: surface-authority

<a id="decision.surface-authority.because"></a>
**Because:** law 7 needs an authored surface

<a id="decision.surface-authority.chosen"></a>
**Chosen:** the composition surface is canonical

**Rejected:**

<a id="decision.surface-authority.rejected.baked-projection.because"></a>
*baked-projection* — **Because:** a stamping projector breaks law 5

<a id="decision.surface-authority.rejected.read-only-lens.because"></a>
*read-only-lens* — **Because:** you cannot compose a harness you only mirror
